在虚拟赤坂闪电战中举办的音乐节“META = Knot 2024”的第二位艺术家发布！永濑裕花、Kiu、SOMUNIA 登场https://www.moguravr.com/metaknot-2024-in-Akasaka-blitz-2/ノンジャンル人生 Fri, 16 Feb 2024 02:00:16 +0000 VRChatVTuberメタバース赤坂ブリッツ https://www.moguravr.com/?p=245988 <p> VRChat Metaverse 音乐节赤坂闪电战 Meta = Knot 2024 第二位艺人已发布。 META = Knot 2024 是一个活生生的圣地“红色 […] 于 2020 年 9 月关闭</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/metaknot-2024-in-akasaka-blitz-2/">在后虚拟赤坂闪电战中举办的音乐节“META = KNOT 2024”的第二位艺术家发布了！ Yuhana Nagase、Kinu 和 Somunia 首次出现</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> <a href="https://hello.vrchat.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VRChat</a> Metaverse 音乐节<strong>赤坂闪电战 Meta = Knot 2024</strong>第二位艺人已发布。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/95641891912ac1f8990c82f35e0cb189-kix.k6rz6jl0h902-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/95641891912ac1f8990c82f35e0cb189-kix.k6rz6jl0h902-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/95641891912ac1f8990c82f35e0cb189-kix.k6rz6jl0h902-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/95641891912ac1f8990c82f35e0cb189-kix.k6rz6jl0h902-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/95641891912ac1f8990c82f35e0cb189-kix.k6rz6jl0h902-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/95641891912ac1f8990c82f35e0cb189-kix.k6rz6jl0h902-jpg.webp 1200w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> META = Knot 2024是在虚拟空间再现2020年9月闭幕的现场圣地“赤坂BLITZ”的音乐节。共有 16 名虚拟歌手出现，第一期中公布了<a href="https://twitter.com/sana_natori" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>名取纱奈</strong></a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/harusaruhi" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>春沙鲁</strong></a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/KOKO__virtual" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>小津</strong></a>。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/95641891912a