 “ VTUBER KOSHIEN”参与成员摘要流行的VTUBER和其他人出现在集团和公司个人之外[2月19日的Postscript] https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-koshien-2024-member/ノンジャンル人生 Thu, 15 Feb 2024 05:58:02 +0000 VTuberVTuber甲子園 https://www.moguravr.com/?p=245906 <p> “ Vtuber Koshien”是一个受欢迎的VTUBER和其他团体和公司个人团体，并且反对活着强大的职业棒球。每个团队都开始训练团队，并且第一年的球员可以使用。 “ Vtuber Koshien”是EBA […]</p><p>帖子“ Vtuber Koshien”参与成员<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">受欢迎的</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-koshien-2024-member/">VTubers出现在团体和企业个人之外的游戏中</a></p>; <p> <strong>“ Vtuber Koshien”是</strong>一个受欢迎的VTUBER和其他团体和公司个人团体，并且反对活着强大的职业棒球。每个团队都开始训练团队，并且第一年的球员可以使用。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> “ VTUBER KOSHIEN”是面对VTUBER和其他由<a href="https://www.konami.com/pawa/2022/powerful" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ebaseball强大的Pro Baseball 2022</a> （2023 Update Update）创建的团队的计划。这次是<a href="https://neo-porte.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Neo-Porte</strong></a> ，来自Nijisanji的<a href="https://twitter.com/ShibuyaHAL" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Haru Shibuya</strong></a> ， <a href="https://twitter.com/yuika_siina" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Yuka</strong></a> <a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Shiina</strong></a> ，来自<a href="https://hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Holo Live</strong></a>到<a href="https://twitter.com/hakuikoyori" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Hiroi</strong></a> Ko，以及来自个人的<a href="https://twitter.com/tenkaitukasa" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Tenji</strong></a> 。</p><p>在皇冠九开始时，一开始有六个新学生，每个学生都有一个角色构成。一些专业棒球运动员的转世球员加入了。但是，在Vtuber Koshien中，重置一开始有多达两个规则，拥有一支理想的团队非常幸运。在完成夏季团队的第三年之前，还值得注意的是，每个高中的成员都会聚集。</p><p> * 2月19日的后记：描述所有团队的第二年成员</p><h2>Hololive高中</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>主任：Hiroi KO</p><p> [第一年]<br />・宝藏海军陆战队（投手）<br />・ Hubuki Shirakami（投手）<br />・ Miko Sakura（捕手）<br />・拉普拉斯黑暗（外野手）<br />・ Ayame Hyakki（外野手）<br /> sora（外野手）的时间</p><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-768x432.webp 768w" wid